title: Method Statement for Installation of G.I Boxes
description:
Method Statement for Installation of G.I Boxes is electrical engineering documentation suitable for MEP construction works.

Document Summary: This method of statement covers the installation of boxes as defined in the General Specification. This procedure will define the method to be used to ensure that boxes installations and workmanship are correct and acceptable and shall conform to the Contract Documents and Specification.
